OL,6,FITV West Country's Caron Bell has been
OL,7,Fto Limpley Stoke to ahead of the
OL,8,Fclosure
OL,10,FA busy A road is closing for more than
OL,11,Fsix months for repairs after cracks
OL,12,Fstarted to appear.
OL,14,FThe A36 Warminster Road will be fully
OL,15,Fclosed between Limpley Stoke and
OL,16,FMonkton Combe from 12 August until
OL,17,Fspring 2025.
