OL,3,CBusy A road will close for more than
OL,4,Csix months for repairs
OL,6,FWork is required to stabilise the
OL,7,Fsouthbound embankment following
OL,8,Fcracking in the footpath alongside the
OL,9,Fcarriageway.
OL,11,FThis will prevent further movement and
OL,12,Fkeep the main carriageway safe.
OL,14,FDuring the closure, National Highways
OL,15,Fwill also make improvements to the
OL,16,Fdrainage to prevent future damage and
OL,17,Freduce the need for more closures.
OL,19,FAll diversion routes have been agreed
OL,20,Fto keep disruption as minimum as
OL,21,Fpossible.
