OL,6,FWhile work is carried out, access will
OL,7,Fbe maintained to properties within the
OL,8,Fclosure, with traffic marshals on hand
OL,9,Fto help.
OL,11,FHugh Campbell, senior project manager
OL,12,Ffor National Highways, said: "Safety
OL,13,Fis our number one priority and we
OL,14,Fapologise for any inconvenience this
OL,15,Fmay cause but need to fix the root of
OL,16,Fthe problem to ensure it doesn't
OL,17,Fhappen again and that motorists and
OL,18,Fpedestrians remain safe at all times.
