OL,6,F"We understand that road closures are
OL,7,Ffrustrating, but by fully closing the
OL,8,Froad, we can get this scheme done
OL,9,Fsafely and quickly, causing less
OL,10,Fdisruption overall. Once it's all
OL,11,Fcomplete, these improvements will
OL,12,Fbenefit road users and the local
OL,13,Fcommunity for many years to come."
