OL,6,FCouncillor Manda Rigby, cabinet member
OL,7,Ffor transport at Bath and North East
OL,8,FSomerset Council, said: "Unfortunately
OL,9,Fthese are significant works to repair
OL,10,Fan ongoing issue that will be
OL,11,Fdisruptive for a period of time but
OL,12,Fwhat National Highways are doing is
OL,13,Fabsolutely essential.
OL,15,F"We've worked closely with National
OL,16,FHighways to make sure suitable
OL,17,Fdiversions are put in place, the works
OL,18,Fcause as little disruption as possible
OL,19,Fand that residents will be kept
OL,20,Finformed throughout the project."
